# macOS Finder copy-on-duplicate files ("foo 2.json", "bar 2.tsx", etc.)
# They show up whenever you drag-duplicate something in Finder. Caught
# during Phase 4 commit (Session 4.5, 2026-05).
* 2.*
* 2
* 3.*
* 3
